{"tid":635363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人愈大愈少朋友","createTime":"2018-04-20T05:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-21T15:21:38.000Z","uid":66957,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c618a8c238a219ef648a8f929784d3e5cc3bd67b","tid":635363,"uid":66957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"以前細個中學雖然唔係咩交際高手<br />\n但都叫有自己嘅朋友圈子<br />\n人大左 出黎做野<br />\n朋友愈黎愈少 慢慢冇晒聯絡<br />\n又識唔到新朋友<br />\n初初都會好介意 覺得朋友係需要好多先開心<br />\n但慢慢就覺得其實冇咩大不了<br />\n再慢慢同餘下嘅幾個最fd嘅朋友有啲衝突<br />\n到宜家我有時係到諗<br />\n其實冇晒朋友都係一個唔錯嘅選擇 <br />\n唔洗再為佢地唔開心 唔洗再煩<br />\n<br />\n有冇人同我一樣？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecacb5f2d9a6072574c6c00754818a454982acb1","tid":635363,"uid":134484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:19:26.000Z","msg":"年經post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f464e08c3e4afeff73a75c0084ee0bba62e2a8","tid":635363,"uid":13374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:40:17.000Z","msg":"已經習慣冇咩朋友"},{"pid":"d558e3af1797f9a82e6ad856195e6cd026306a7d","tid":635363,"uid":157099,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T05:58:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ac56aa9eba72a661062f6752fdb11c2c3e1b8fae","tid":635363,"uid":57835,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T06:01:07.000Z","msg":"上到大專先有朋友，到而家都係同一班"},{"pid":"18844c5224cf9125131258eee0833492d8956bfb","tid":635363,"uid":182567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"我而家keep到果班朋友都係10年前果班, 我都想識新朋友"},{"pid":"bf05eb5fcdd322ad19e2e56d081eecc83f5b9da7","tid":635363,"uid":66957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"18844c5224cf9125131258eee0833492d8956bfb","tid":635363,"uid":182567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:39:06.000Z","msg":"我而家keep到果班朋友都係10年前果班, 我都想識新朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T08:43:1